Installation
------------

For installing ExGUtils, just download it, extract the .tar.bz2 in a 
folder and run the setup by typing "python setup.py install", as root.
Answer if you want C sources compiled or just the python functions.
Some users reported dificulties in compiling C sources in windows. 
The python functions perform the same tasks, but have worst numerical
precision and efficiency. 



